Or are you alone,
as I am?

587
00:39:18,266 --> 00:39:20,347
I have a mother
and a sister.

588
00:39:22,546 --> 00:39:23,744
Dear God!

589
00:39:24,106 --> 00:39:26,906
If he has sent me here,
what has he done to Kate?

590
00:39:27,506 --> 00:39:29,059
I'm grateful
that you came.

591
00:39:29,146 --> 00:39:31,064
It is a boon
to a single man

592
00:39:31,147 --> 00:39:34,110
to have such
a lady as yourself for my hostess.

593
00:39:34,147 --> 00:39:36,832
I know little
of how these things are done in London.

594
00:39:36,907 --> 00:39:40,110
Surely one of
the other ladies would be more adept.

595
00:39:40,747 --> 00:39:42,866
You are the only
lady present.

596
00:39:44,027 --> 00:39:47,067
By the time I was finished
with her, she couldn't escape.

597
00:39:54,387 --> 00:39:56,823
Have you thought
about the investment I brought you?

598
00:39:57,467 --> 00:40:00,583
Uh, well,
it has its merits and its risks.

599
00:40:01,107 --> 00:40:02,746
