Well, I like to
keep a clear head.

603
00:40:08,187 --> 00:40:09,548
Yet you pour us
so much.

604
00:40:09,907 --> 00:40:12,707
Nickleby, I must say,
it is a pleasure having your niece with us.

605
00:40:12,787 --> 00:40:14,350
He must have
designed that, too,

606
00:40:14,427 --> 00:40:16,230
to soften you
into speculating.

607
00:40:16,307 --> 00:40:18,752
If I could see
someone as winning as Miss Nickleby

608
00:40:18,787 --> 00:40:20,503
when I come
to her uncle's to talk business,

609
00:40:20,587 --> 00:40:23,310
I can think of no other place
I would rather talk business.

610
00:40:23,508 --> 00:40:26,145
No other place on earth.

611
00:40:26,747 --> 00:40:28,703
Hear, hear, hear!

612
00:40:30,788 --> 00:40:33,665
Gentlemen, I feel
we are boring Miss Nickleby.

613
00:40:33,748 --> 00:40:36,500
Look, she can barely
raise her eyes.

614
00:40:36,587 --> 00:40:39,301
The poor,
dear girl simply cannot understand

615
00:40:39,388 --> 00:40:41,181
why no one here
is making love to her.

616
00:40:42,268 --> 00:40:45,308
She gasps!
I have uncovered her secret.

617
00:40:46,828 --> 00:40:48,544
No!
You misunderstand me. I...

618
00:40:48,628 --> 00:40:50,948
In fact, I'll hold
any man 50 pounds

619
00:40:51,028 --> 00:40:53,348
that Miss Nickleby
can't look in my face

620
00:40:53,428 --> 00:40:55,547
and tell me that
she wasn't thinking so.

621
00:40:55,588 --> 00:40:57,506
Done, done, done!

622
00:40:57,628 --> 00:40:58,663
Done!

623
00:40:59,148 --> 00:41:02,111
Pray, do not make me
the subject of bets.

624
00:41:02,668 --> 00:41:03,991
Uncle, please!

625
