Why not,
if the gentlemen insist?

626
00:41:07,308 --> 00:41:08,631
It's a minute's work.

627
00:41:08,668 --> 00:41:10,710
Just lift your eyes
and tell me

628
00:41:10,748 --> 00:41:13,462
that you're not
hoping I would make love to you.

629
