682
00:44:45,193 --> 00:44:47,552
His mother could
fire a pistol

683
00:44:47,593 --> 00:44:49,511
and get in bed
wearing a nightcap.

684
00:44:49,833 --> 00:44:50,955
But...

685
00:44:51,513 --> 00:44:53,431
There is tragedy
in the family.

686
00:44:54,673 --> 00:44:56,514
In the pony's family?

687
00:44:56,833 --> 00:44:57,993
Yes.

688
00:44:58,313 --> 00:45:00,231
The father drank.

689
00:45:00,833 --> 00:45:02,914
